title: OMC Crosses Above Key Moving Average Level - Nasdaq.com
text: In trading on Thursday, shares of Omnicom Group, Inc. (Symbol: OMC) crossed above their 200 day moving average of $77.34, changing hands as high as $78.20 per share. Omnicom Group, Inc. shares are currently trading up about 1.9% on the day. The chart below shows the one year performance of OMC shares, versus its 200 day moving average:     Looking at the chart above, OMC's low point in its 52 week range is $65.85 per share, with $85.05 as the 52 week high point - that compares with a last trade of $78.12.
